value: Shallow marshes, and wet meadows; in winter, drier fresh-water and brackish marshes, as well as dense, deep grass, and rice fields.
breeding, higher, drier margins of fresh-and brackish-water marshes dominated by sedges & grasses;also swampy meadows, sedge meadows, occasly wet, cut-over hay fields;winters coastal marshes
